{
  "comment": "Vercel project config",
  "notes": [
    "What goes here:",
    "  - rewrites: map /api/* to serverless functions in /api/",
    "  - env: reference environment variables (SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_ANON_KEY)",
    "  - headers: CORS headers so the frontend can call /api/jobs",
    "  - Example structure:",
    "    {",
    "      'rewrites': [{ 'source': '/api/(.*)', 'destination': '/api/$1' }],",
    "      'headers': [{ 'source': '/api/(.*)', 'headers': [{ 'key': 'Access-Control-Allow-Origin', 'value': '*' }] }]",
    "    }"
  ]
}
